{
  "videoId": "6tvW_gVcidg",
  "sceneNum": 1,
  "lyrics": [
    {
      "t": 49.96,
      "end": 54.96,
      "text": "File 82-712, Agent Rick Dicker interrogating."
    },
    {
      "t": 54.96,
      "end": 56.96,
      "text": "State your name, please."
    },
    {
      "t": 57.96,
      "end": 59.96,
      "text": "Uh, Tony?"
    },
    {
      "t": 59.96,
      "end": 61.96,
      "text": "Tony Ridinger?"
    },
    {
      "t": 63.96,
      "end": 65.96,
      "text": "Tell me about the incident."
    },
    {
      "t": 65.96,
      "end": 68.96,
      "text": "Well, there's this girl in my class."
    },
    {
      "t": 68.96,
      "end": 70.96,
      "text": "I saw her at the track meet."
    },
    {
      "t": 70.96,
      "end": 72.96,
      "text": "You're, uh, Viola, right?"
    },
    {
      "t": 72.96,
      "end": 73.96,
      "text": "That's me."
    },
    {
      "t": 73.96,
      "end": 75.96,
      "text": "I sort of knew her, but she changed."
    },
    {
      "t": 75.96,
      "end": 77.96,
      "text": "Relaxed. She was more sure of herself."
    },
    {
      "t": 77.96,
      "end": 78.96,
      "text": "Cool. Cute."
    },
    {
      "t": 78.96,
      "end": 80.96,
      "text": "I asked her out to a movie."
    },
    {
      "t": 80.96,
      "end": 81.96,
      "text": "So, Friday?"
    },
    {
      "t": 81.96,
      "end": 82.96,
      "text": "Friday."
    },
    {
      "t": 82.96,
      "end": 84.96,
      "text": "And I went to watch the movie."
    },
    {
      "t": 84.96,
      "end": 85.96,
      "text": "Friday?"
    },
    {
      "t": 85.96,
      "end": 86.96,
      "text": "Friday."
    },
    {
      "t": 86.96,
      "end": 88.96,
      "text": "And I went to watch the track meet."
    },
    {
      "t": 88.96,
      "end": 92.96,
      "text": "Not long after, this thing happened in the parking lot."
    },
    {
      "t": 104.96,
      "end": 108.96,
      "text": "Behold the Underminer!"
    },
    {
      "t": 108.96,
      "end": 111.96,
      "text": "I have no place beneath you!"
    },
    {
      "t": 112.96,
      "end": 114.96,
      "text": "As if things aren't weird enough,"
    },
    {
      "t": 114.96,
      "end": 116.96,
      "text": "I look over and I see these boots."
    },
    {
      "t": 116.96,
      "end": 117.96,
      "text": "You two stay here."
    },
    {
      "t": 117.96,
      "end": 119.96,
      "text": "Wait, should we be doing this?"
    },
    {
      "t": 119.96,
      "end": 120.96,
      "text": "It is still illegal."
    },
    {
      "t": 120.96,
      "end": 122.96,
      "text": "They look like superheroes."
    },
    {
      "t": 122.96,
      "end": 123.96,
      "text": "We're gonna lose it."
    },
    {
      "t": 123.96,
      "end": 124.96,
      "text": "Oh, all right."
    },
    {
      "t": 124.96,
      "end": 125.96,
      "text": "One of you patrol the perimeter."
    },
    {
      "t": 125.96,
      "end": 126.96,
      "text": "Keep the crowds back and safe."
    },
    {
      "t": 126.96,
      "end": 127.96,
      "text": "The other, watch after Jack-Jack."
    },
    {
      "t": 127.96,
      "end": 128.96,
      "text": "But I thought we were gonna go..."
    },
    {
      "t": 128.96,
      "end": 130.96,
      "text": "You heard your mother!"
    },
    {
      "t": 130.96,
      "end": 131.96,
      "text": "Trampoline me."
    },
    {
      "t": 136.96,
      "end": 137.96,
      "text": "I saw a perimeter!"
    },
    {
      "t": 137.96,
      "end": 138.96,
      "text": "We're not going anywhere!"
    },
    {
      "t": 138.96,
      "end": 140.96,
      "text": "It's an Omagate Creek!"
    },
    {
      "t": 140.96,
      "end": 142.96,
      "text": "I see my chance to get out of there."
    },
    {
      "t": 142.96,
      "end": 144.96,
      "text": "But there's something familiar"
    },
    {
      "t": 144.96,
      "end": 146.96,
      "text": "about one of the kids' voices."
    },
    {
      "t": 146.96,
      "end": 149.96,
      "text": "The girl, she's upset and she throws down her mask and..."
    },
    {
      "t": 149.96,
      "end": 150.96,
      "text": "And it's her!"
    },
    {
      "t": 150.96,
      "end": 152.96,
      "text": "Oh, Tony!"
    },
    {
      "t": 152.96,
      "end": 153.96,
      "text": "Hi."
    },
    {
      "t": 153.96,
      "end": 155.96,
      "text": "Uh, this isn't what you think it is."
    },
    {
      "t": 155.96,
      "end": 156.96,
      "text": "It was just getting too freaky."
    },
    {
      "t": 156.96,
      "end": 159.96,
      "text": "I couldn't handle it and ran off."
    },
    {
      "t": 159.96,
      "end": 160.96,
      "text": "I feel kind of bad about it."
    },
    {
      "t": 160.96,
      "end": 163.96,
      "text": "Maybe I should have said hi or something?"
    },
    {
      "t": 163.96,
      "end": 165.96,
      "text": "It's not her fault superheroes are illegal."
    },
    {
      "t": 165.96,
      "end": 167.96,
      "text": "And it's not like I don't like strong girls."
    },
    {
      "t": 167.96,
      "end": 169.96,
      "text": "I'm pretty secure, manhood-wise."
    },
    {
      "t": 169.96,
      "end": 170.96,
      "text": "What is that?"
    },
    {
      "t": 170.96,
      "end": 172.96,
      "text": "Have you told anyone else about this?"
    },
    {
      "t": 172.96,
      "end": 173.96,
      "text": "Your parents?"
    },
    {
      "t": 173.96,
      "end": 175.96,
      "text": "No, they'd only think I was hiding something."
    },
    {
      "t": 175.96,
      "end": 176.96,
      "text": "You know what I mean?"
    },
    {
      "t": 176.96,
      "end": 177.96,
      "text": "Sure, kid."
    },
    {
      "t": 177.96,
      "end": 179.96,
      "text": "I like this girl, Mr. Digger."
    },
    {
      "t": 179.96,
      "end": 181.96,
      "text": "I'm supposed to go out with her Friday night."
    },
    {
      "t": 181.96,
      "end": 184.96,
      "text": "Now things are just gonna be weird."
    },
    {
      "t": 184.96,
      "end": 187.96,
      "text": "I wish I could forget I ever saw her in that suit."
    },
    {
      "t": 187.96,
      "end": 189.96,
      "text": "You will, kid."
    },
    {
      "t": 189.96,
      "end": 191.96,
      "text": "You will."
    },
    {
      "t": 191.96,
      "end": 193.96,
      "text": "You will."
    }
  ],
